            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-d32ea995-b539-49b3-bc00-2cda174100d9">
                The Lord Privy Seal (Mr. Attlee)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-d32ea995-b539-49b3-bc00-2cda174100d9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
