            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-9844482b-1f6c-4c3c-849e-122a6e8c39e1" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
